text: Luca Gádorfalvi (born 29 January 1976) is a Hungarian windsurfer. She competed in the 2000 Summer Olympics. She is also the sister of Áron Gádorfalvi. ==References== Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:Sailors at the 2000 Summer Olympics – Mistral One Design Category:Hungarian female sailors (sport) Category:Hungarian windsurfers Category:Olympic sailors of Hungary
